snippet.title: Mika and The Witch's Mountain Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Mika and The Witch's Mountain is a combat-free game about an aspiring witch. Earn upgrades with each successful delivery and get to know all of the quirky characters in town. Be careful, though: "Flying is a dangerous business, and packages are easily damaged!" https://store.steampowered.com/app/1819460/Mika_and_The_Witchs_Mountain/ #indiegames #witch #cozygames
